## Get categories [/categories]

### Get categories [GET]
Get list of available categories

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        ["action", "crime", "drama", "..."]

## Get information of a movie [/movie-infos/{id}]

+ parameters

    + id: 5e9350b39991040ec52bf698 (required, string) - Movie's ID

### Get information of a movie [GET]
Get information of a movie

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes(MovieData)
    
## Search movies [/search{?query}{?category}{?limit}{?page}{?provider}{?sort}]

### Search movies [GET]
Get all movies with specific filters or not

+ parameters

    + query: I saw the Devil (optional, string) - Search query
    + category: action (optional, string) - Name of the category
    + limit: 20 (optional, number) - Number of movies by page
    + page: 3 (optional, number) - Page's number (Starts at 1)
    + provider: yts (optional, ProviderList) - Name of the provider
    + sort: year (optional, SortList) - The sort option

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes(array[MovieData], fixed-type)

